  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Start in Operations and look down the sidebar.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 2.653,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "The whole module is laid out in three groups.",
      "startS": 3.333,
      "endS": 5.639,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "Maintenance sits at the top, then Incident Reports, then the Scheduler pages.",
      "startS": 6.14,
      "endS": 7.43,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "We are in Maintenance, where five entries stack together.",
      "startS": 7.857,
      "endS": 10.73,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "The first is Issues, the work-order list you already know.",
      "startS": 11.596,
      "endS": 14.512,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "The four below it are the planned side of upkeep,",
      "startS": 15.106,
      "endS": 18.341,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "the routines and gear and parts that sit behind every ticket.",
      "startS": 18.889,
      "endS": 21.244,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "That set is today's tour.",
      "startS": 21.59,
      "endS": 27.079,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "Click Maintenance Schedule.",
      "startS": 27.567,
      "endS": 28.937,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "This is the planned side of upkeep.",
      "startS": 29.634,
      "endS": 31.508,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "Forty two recurring tasks live on this calendar, six due this week and two already overdue.",
      "startS": 31.98,
      "endS": 37.769,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Each row is a job that repeats:",
      "startS": 38.442,
      "endS": 40.215,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "lubricate the conveyor chain weekly, inspect the chemical pumps once a month.",
      "startS": 40.553,
      "endS": 42.339,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "The column a manager reads first is Next Due,",
      "startS": 42.648,
      "endS": 44.734,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "because it names the service that is coming before anything breaks.",
      "startS": 45.39,
      "endS": 51.84,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "Now Equipment Registry.",
      "startS": 52.313,
      "endS": 54.019,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "Every machine a work order points back to.",
      "startS": 54.401,
      "endS": 56.935,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "This tenant carries four assets:",
      "startS": 57.168,
      "endS": 59.125,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "a blower system, a chemical pump array, the main tunnel conveyor, and a point of sale terminal.",
      "startS": 59.351,
      "endS": 60.304,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "Three are operational and one sits in repair.",
      "startS": 60.518,
      "endS": 64.943,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "When a caller says the air dryer is down,",
      "startS": 65.204,
      "endS": 67.894,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "this page names the exact unit, places it at its site, and shows whether it is already flagged.",
      "startS": 68.158,
      "endS": 76.08,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "Open Checklists.",
      "startS": 76.589,
      "endS": 77.286,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "These are the fixed steps a tech follows so nothing gets skipped on a busy day.",
      "startS": 77.286,
      "endS": 83.869,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "Daily opening and closing walks, a weekly safety inspection, a monthly deep clean.",
      "startS": 83.869,
      "endS": 88.959,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "The completion column shows how faithfully each one gets done,",
      "startS": 88.959,
      "endS": 92.708,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "and the average sits at ninety four percent.",
      "startS": 92.708,
      "endS": 96.177,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "One caution.",
      "startS": 96.177,
      "endS": 96.874,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "This is not the Lube Checklists page over in Hardware settings.",
      "startS": 96.874,
      "endS": 101.005,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "Different place, different job.",
      "startS": 101.005,
      "endS": 102.399,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "Last one. Parts and Supplies.",
      "startS": 102.955,
      "endS": 105.074,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "The stock a repair pulls from.",
      "startS": 105.753,
      "endS": 107.532,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "Drive belts, pump seal kits, dryer filters, a spare power supply.",
      "startS": 108.046,
      "endS": 108.897,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "A hundred forty two parts, about eighteen thousand dollars sitting on the shelf.",
      "startS": 109.146,
      "endS": 112.81,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "Read quantity on hand against the reorder point",
      "startS": 113.259,
      "endS": 117.46,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "and you can answer a do we have it call in seconds.",
      "startS": 117.826,
      "endS": 123.663,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "And keep it straight from Chemicals and Supplies over in Inventory;",
      "startS": 124.005,
      "endS": 127.177,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "that page is wash chemistry and retail goods, this one is upkeep.",
      "startS": 127.454,
      "endS": 132.351,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "So, the map.",
      "startS": 132.351,
      "endS": 133.289,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "Four live pages under Maintenance, right beside Issues.",
      "startS": 134.017,
      "endS": 137.719,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "A recurring job lands on the Schedule, and Next Due says when.",
      "startS": 138.487,
      "endS": 140.483,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "A question about a machine goes to the Registry.",
      "startS": 140.772,
      "endS": 142.348,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "The steps a tech follows are the Checklists.",
      "startS": 143.029,
      "endS": 145.466,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "The parts a repair burns through are Parts and Supplies.",
      "startS": 146.15,
      "endS": 148.712,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "One habit before you go.",
      "startS": 149.243,
      "endS": 152.578,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "Reach these pages from the sidebar inside Operations,",
      "startS": 153.518,
      "endS": 154.979,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "because typing an address straight into the browser still fails.",
      "startS": 155.584,
      "endS": 162.446,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "The sidebar is the front door.",
      "startS": 163.094,
      "endS": 164.88,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}